            "answer_text": "Application for leave of absence Suppose, your name is Aditi Singh, and you\u2019re a student of Bluebells School International, Delhi. You couldn\u2019t attend the school for two days. Below is an example of writing an application for leave of absence to the Principal of your school. 28 November 2019 To, The Principal Bluebells School International, Delhi. Subject: Application for leave of absence. Sir/ma'am, I am Aditi Singh, student of class IX A. With due respect, I would like to inform you that I could not attend school on 25th and 26th of November 2020 due to high fever/cold/stomachache/headache/viral infection. I, therefore, request you to kindly grant me a leave of absence for those two days. Yours obediently Aditi Singh Class - IX A Roll No: Seven ",
